summary: My test dungeon I made whilst Learning the CK
descriptionHtml:
Named it what I did because its fucking psychotic.

This is just a 3 stage rudimentary dungeon i scrapped together learning the CK.

First stage is just a nord ruin into a cave, second stage is where the shit hits the fan, I got a little carried away and you might need to console TIM for invuln, but watching the scene play out is pretty epic imo.

Sometimes the dragons win, sometimes the atronochs win, sometimes the humans win, but NEVER do the skeletons win. 
(I KNOW THE FUCKING DRAGONS FLY THROUGH WALLS AND SHIT THEY ARE CHUCK NORRIS NINJA DAGRONS!!, so ya... i gave up and just made it work lol)

3rd stage is just a dwarven ruin.

I did not really clutter these up or trap them it was just me learning how to do those etc

I have hit a brick wall on scripting, so if anyone wants to help make some quest mods etc I can design levels populate clutter trap them and provide voice actors. I can do the dialogue trees etc in quest editor but I seriously suck at scripting. My brain hurt after a hour of trying to figure it out. 

Video (IT IS A SPOILER DO NOT WATCH AMG!!!) http://www.twitch.tv/maveric83eq/b/314710950
Ya you hear my friend in vent yapping cause I was streaming for him. 

Anyway enjoy
